            "answer_text": "Medical imaging Medical imaging is an essential step in the cancer diagnosis process.Imaging is typically performed after positive results in simpler tests such as blood tests.Imaging enables visualization of the size, shape, and location of the tumor.The images can be used to guide endoscopy and tumor biopsy.",
